description:
In the futuristic world of WebtrES Club, where robots and humans coexist, there was a unique and specialized robot named Oscilla. Oscilla was designed to resemble an old-fashioned oscilloscope, with its box-like metallic body and a large broken screen in the center. This robot was unlike any other in the club, known for its exceptional skills as a soldier and its peculiar attachment to cats.
